STIFF is a program that convert scientific FITS images to the
more popular TIFF format.

This file describes shortly the SYNTAX of STIFF.
See INSTALL for instructions about install.
For more information, please refer to the documentation
in doc/

The general SYNTAX of STIFF is:

% stiff <fits_image1>  [<fits_image2> <fits_image3>]
	[-c <configuration_file>] [-<keyword> <value>]

Please report any bug or strange behaviour to http://astromatic.net/forum .

					Emmanuel Bertin.

